36:04.162 --> 36:06.296
â™ª

36:27.451 --> 36:30.687
The last ship I took was made
from over 600 oak trees.

36:30.689 --> 36:33.490
And the one we're waiting on
will be staffed by 311 men.

36:33.492 --> 36:36.359
You certainly
love boats, don't you?
Love them.

36:36.361 --> 36:38.962
Completely.
Ours has 75 cabins,

36:38.964 --> 36:40.931
With mine being the most
ornate, of course, as king.

36:40.933 --> 36:42.465
Seven gun ports,

36:42.467 --> 36:43.667
82 guns, including--

36:43.669 --> 36:45.335
W... I'm-I'm sorry.

36:45.337 --> 36:47.204
Did you say you're a king?

36:47.206 --> 36:48.805
From the kingdom of imereti,

36:48.807 --> 36:50.473
Uh, near russia
and the black sea.

36:50.475 --> 36:52.609
I've been studying abroad,
but I'm making my way

36:52.611 --> 36:54.611
Back home,
because my father just died.

36:54.613 --> 36:56.980
You should attend
the coronation.

36:56.982 --> 37:00.383
Well, I can't, at the moment.

37:00.385 --> 37:02.652
But, uh, perhaps

37:02.654 --> 37:04.721
You and I could
write to one another,

37:04.723 --> 37:06.856
Be pen pals?
And...

37:06.858 --> 37:10.260
Sometime in the next
few months, say...

37:10.262 --> 37:12.762
This winter, maybe I could

37:12.764 --> 37:15.365
Come and visit you.
I could use a pal.

37:15.367 --> 37:18.235
They say it's lonely
being king.
Well, it doesn't have to be.

37:18.237 --> 37:19.502
Not in my experience.

37:20.638 --> 37:22.539
Or at least
not for long, anyway.

37:22.541 --> 37:25.775
So you'll be a man
soon enough, won't you?

37:25.777 --> 37:27.877
I hope so.

37:27.879 --> 37:29.913
Listen, when I come
to visit you,

37:29.915 --> 37:32.616
Would it be all right if brought
my sister's baby with me?

37:32.618 --> 37:34.751
Sure.
Wonderful.

37:34.753 --> 37:37.954
And in the meantime, we have
a whole journey across the sea

37:37.956 --> 37:41.491
To become very good friends.

37:57.308 --> 37:58.908
Delphine...

37:58.910 --> 38:00.577
But they took you away.

38:00.579 --> 38:01.845
How are you here?

38:01.847 --> 38:02.979
That murdered boy--

38:02.981 --> 38:04.314
I never harmed him,

38:04.316 --> 38:06.716
But I did have sex with him.

38:06.718 --> 38:08.485
Cold passion
mixed with your

38:08.487 --> 38:09.686
Warm blood.

38:09.688 --> 38:11.354
It was to bind you to me.

38:12.423 --> 38:14.057
A spell, you mean?

38:14.059 --> 38:16.559
Black magic?

38:16.561 --> 38:17.961
It was to nurture
what was growing

38:17.963 --> 38:19.362
Between us.

38:19.364 --> 38:20.864
The bond we have

38:20.866 --> 38:22.766
And the future
I saw for us.

38:22.768 --> 38:24.501
And it worked.

38:24.503 --> 38:27.404
Without harming
another, it worked.

38:27.406 --> 38:29.039
We are linked.
My spirit is inside you now,

38:29.041 --> 38:31.841
As yours is in mine.

38:31.843 --> 38:33.543
What do you mean?

38:33.545 --> 38:35.945
(echoing):
They're burning me.

38:37.081 --> 38:38.748
Cardinal:
For the charges of murder,

38:38.750 --> 38:40.450
Ritual sacrifice,

38:40.452 --> 38:42.485
Transformation
and devil worship,

38:42.487 --> 38:44.421
I condemn you, witch,

38:44.423 --> 38:45.989
To death by fire.

38:45.991 --> 38:49.926
(screaming)

38:51.329 --> 38:52.495
(screaming)

38:56.701 --> 38:57.767
Aah!

38:58.669 --> 39:00.036
My lord, are you unwell?

39:00.038 --> 39:01.771
I feel like I'm on fire.

39:04.842 --> 39:07.344
(hissing)
get back, witch!

39:07.346 --> 39:08.411
Man:
She's getting away!

39:09.580 --> 39:11.081
Man:
Get her!

39:21.692 --> 39:24.127
I will love you
for the rest of my life.

39:24.129 --> 39:26.396
And I will never
let you go again.

39:36.140 --> 39:38.808
Francis:
<i>I hope she's pregnant soon.</i>

39:38.810 --> 39:40.710
A child is vital,
and it will help

39:40.712 --> 39:42.779
Protect her in France as well.

39:42.781 --> 39:45.849
(groans quietly)

39:45.851 --> 39:49.018
The pain of your illness
never relented?

39:49.020 --> 39:52.555
Your herbs have helped a great
deal, nostradamus, but...

39:54.558 --> 39:56.626
I'm dying.

39:59.397 --> 40:01.398
Yes.

40:01.400 --> 40:03.466
You are.

40:06.871 --> 40:08.938
â™ª

40:21.018 --> 40:23.953
Man: Her majesty
queen elizabeth.

40:28.426 --> 40:30.026
Catherine de medici.

40:30.028 --> 40:32.929
What a pleasure
to meet one so legendary.

40:32.931 --> 40:34.831
Ah, thank you, your majes...
Common lore is that your

40:34.833 --> 40:36.099
Teeth are filed into points

40:36.101 --> 40:38.067
And your eyes
are black with rage.

40:38.069 --> 40:40.870
And yet here you are,
as lovely as a sunny day.

40:40.872 --> 40:43.440
You radiate warmth
and beauty yourself.

40:43.442 --> 40:46.042
Though I know that you are
personally responsible

40:46.044 --> 40:48.678
For the death of nearly
a thousand men in France,

40:48.680 --> 40:50.580
Just this month alone.

40:50.582 --> 40:52.482
My son was nearly one of them.

40:52.484 --> 40:53.783
Oh, you mustn't
listen to gossip.

40:53.785 --> 40:56.453
I was told you'd come
to ask something of us.

40:56.455 --> 40:58.087
Ask? No.

40:58.089 --> 41:00.156
I've come to offer
you something.

41:03.761 --> 41:09.532
The destruction of our mutual
enemy: Mary, queen of scots.

